https://blog.csdn.net/ch593030323/article/details/53571807

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ubuntu18.04 qq 微信添加到最上方，需要的插件
sudo apt-get install gnome-shell-extension-top-icons-plus gnome-tweaks

gnome-tweaks打开扩展
打开TopIconPlus 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
进入/usr/share/applications 目录创建 其对应为WeChat.desktop 结尾的文件 
内容如下
创建图标
[Desktop Entry]
Name=WeChat
Exec=/home/tone/Tools/electronic-wechat-linux-x64/electronic-wechat
Comment=WeChat
Icon=/home/tone/Tools/electronic-wechat-linux-x64/wechat.png
Type=Application
Terminal=false
Encoding=UTF-8
Categories=Developer;
------------------------------------------------------
添加qq图标到plank
/home/titanic/.local/share/application/Wine QQ.desktop拖入plank
